videos.headline: Georgia Southern hands Clemson 1st season INT
videos.description: Kindle Vildor intercepts Kelly Bryant's pass to give the Tigers their first turnover of the season.

videos.headline: Bryant sacked on 3rd down
videos.description: Kelly Bryant gets sacked by Georgia Southern's Chris Harris Jr. on 3rd down, followed by a Clemson missed field goal.

videos.headline: Clemson sacks Georgia Southern QB
videos.description: Shai Werts gets taken down by Clemson's Austin Bryant for a loss of seven yards in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Eagles force 2nd Tigers turnover
videos.description: Clemson RB Adam Choice loses the ball after taking the handoff, resulting in another Clemson fumble.

videos.headline: Travis Etienne run for 1 yd for a TD (Greg Huegel KICK)
videos.description: T. Etienne run for 1 yd for a TD, (G. Huegel KICK)

videos.headline: Lawrence connects with Ross for Clemson TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence sails a 57-yard pass to Justyn Ross, who jukes two defenders to make it the end zone.

videos.headline: Feaster leaps into end zone for Clemson TD
videos.description: Tavien Feaster goes airborne to secure another Tigers touchdown against the scoreless Eagles.

videos.headline: Clemson recovers Georgia Southern's drop
videos.description: Nyles Pinckney recovers the Eagles' fumble and returns it 11 yards.

videos.headline: Eagles intercept Clemson's Lawrence
videos.description: Georgia Southern answers Clemson's fumble recovery with an interception on QB Trevor Lawrence in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Eagles capitalize on turnover with TD
videos.description: QB Shai Wertz runs it in himself to secure an Eagles touchdown against Clemson.

videos.headline: C.J. Wright run for 9 yds to the Clem 37
Etienne runs it 40 yards to the house
videos.description: Clemson goes up 31-7 over Georgia Southern with another Travis Etienne touchdown.
